[{"text": "Your final test is a duel.", "start": 0.125, "duration": 2.336}, {"text": "And as a special treat,\nyou may choose your opponent.", "start": 2.753, "duration": 3.879}, {"text": "Point and choose.", "start": 15.724, "duration": 1.46}, {"text": "So you're saying, whoever I point to,\nthat's the person I get to fight?", "start": 17.851, "duration": 4.755}, {"text": "Choose wisely.", "start": 23.815, "duration": 1.585}, {"text": "I...", "start": 27.11, "duration": 1.21}, {"text": "Choose... you!", "start": 29.279, "duration": 2.169}, {"text": "Wrong choice!", "start": 32.658, "duration": 1.96}, {"text": "[screaming]", "start": 38.372, "duration": 1.168}, {"text": "[screaming]", "start": 44.92, "duration": 1.043}, {"text": "[groaning]", "start": 47.297, "duration": 1.252}, {"text": "[laughing]", "start": 52.928, "duration": 1.209}, {"text": "You thought I was a frail old man,", "start": 55.514, "duration": 2.919}, {"text": "but I'm the most powerful earthbender\nyou'll ever see.", "start": 58.517, "duration": 3.712}, {"text": "Can I fight the guy with the axe instead?", "start": 62.813, "duration": 2.085}, {"text": "There are no take-backsies in my kingdom.", "start": 64.982, "duration": 3.169}, {"text": "You might need this.", "start": 68.819, "duration": 1.418}, {"text": "[groaning]", "start": 72.489, "duration": 1.085}, {"text": "Typical airbender tactic,\navoid and evade.", "start": 77.119, "duration": 3.67}, {"text": "I'd hoped the Avatar\nwould be less predictable.", "start": 80.956, "duration": 2.794}, {"text": "[gasping]", "start": 84.501, "duration": 1.043}, {"text": "Don't you have any surprises for me?", "start": 86.17, "duration": 2.419}, {"text": "Sooner or later,\nyou'll have to strike back.", "start": 88.672, "duration": 2.878}, {"text": "[smashing]", "start": 94.469, "duration": 1.043}, {"text": "[thudding]", "start": 97.222, "duration": 1.001}, {"text": "[rumbling]", "start": 103.02, "duration": 1.126}, {"text": "Oh, you'll have to be\na little more creative than that.", "start": 106.899, "duration": 3.295}, {"text": "[booming]", "start": 118.327, "duration": 1.042}, {"text": "Did someone leave the windows open?", "start": 121.33, "duration": 2.419}, {"text": "It feels a little drafty in here.", "start": 124.208, "duration": 2.043}, {"text": "Are you hoping I'll catch a cold?", "start": 126.835, "duration": 2.336}, {"text": "[groaning]", "start": 131.507, "duration": 1.042}, {"text": "[gasping]", "start": 140.307, "duration": 1.043}, {"text": "How are you going to get me\nfrom way over there?", "start": 143.477, "duration": 3.253}, {"text": "[groaning]", "start": 150.901, "duration": 1.043}, {"text": "[screaming]", "start": 166.124, "duration": 1.043}, {"text": "[groaning]", "start": 168.877, "duration": 1.043}, {"text": "[rumbling]", "start": 183.851, "duration": 1.042}, {"text": "[screaming]", "start": 193.485, "duration": 1.043}, {"text": "[wind swirling]", "start": 200.951, "duration": 1.043}, {"text": "[growling]", "start": 206.206, "duration": 1.043}, {"text": "Heh.", "start": 218.427, "duration": 1.042}, {"text": "Well done, Avatar.", "start": 224.016, "duration": 1.877}, {"text": "You fight with much fire in your heart.", "start": 226.185, "duration": 3.003}, {"text": "Huh?", "start": 233.65, "duration": 1.043}, {"text": "You've passed all my tests,\nnow you must answer one question.", "start": 241.408, "duration": 5.547}, {"text": "That's not fair!", "start": 247.331, "duration": 1.042}, {"text": "You said you would release my friends\nif I finished your tests!", "start": 248.457, "duration": 2.794}, {"text": "Oh, but what's the point of tests\nif you don't learn anything?", "start": 251.335, "duration": 3.712}, {"text": "Oh, come on!", "start": 255.13, "duration": 1.251}, {"text": "Answer this one question,\nand I will set your friends free.", "start": 256.798, "duration": 4.463}, {"text": "What... is my name?", "start": 262.095, "duration": 2.044}, {"text": "From the looks of your friends,\nI'd say you only have a few minutes.", "start": 266.058, "duration": 3.795}, {"text": "How am I supposed to know his name?", "start": 271.188, "duration": 1.668}, {"text": "Think about the challenges,\nmaybe it's some kind of riddle.", "start": 273.023, "duration": 2.961}, {"text": "- I got it!\n- Yeah?", "start": 276.068, "duration": 1.168}, {"text": "He's an earthbender, right?", "start": 277.319, "duration": 1.251}, {"text": "Rocky!", "start": 279.029, "duration": 1.043}, {"text": "You know, because of all the rocks!", "start": 281.406, "duration": 1.627}, {"text": "We're gonna keep trying\nbut that is a good back-up.", "start": 283.283, "duration": 2.253}, {"text": "OK, so back to the challenges.", "start": 285.744, "duration": 2.044}, {"text": "I got a key from a waterfall,\nI saved his pet, and I had a duel.", "start": 288.08, "duration": 4.379}, {"text": "And what did you learn?", "start": 292.668, "duration": 1.042}, {"text": "Well, everything was different\nthan I expected.", "start": 293.794, "duration": 3.211}, {"text": "And...", "start": 297.589, "duration": 1.043}, {"text": "Well, they weren't straight forward.", "start": 299.55, "duration": 2.669}, {"text": "To solve each test, I had to think\ndifferently than I usually would.", "start": 302.594, "duration": 3.796}, {"text": "I know his name!", "start": 307.516, "duration": 1.335}, {"text": "I solved the question\nthe same way I solved the challenges.", "start": 311.144, "duration": 3.045}, {"text": "As you said a long time ago,", "start": 314.857, "duration": 1.793}, {"text": "I had to open my brain\nto the possibilities.", "start": 317.234, "duration": 2.419}, {"text": "[laughing]", "start": 320.445, "duration": 1.043}, {"text": "Bumi, you're a mad genius.", "start": 323.24, "duration": 2.461}, {"text": "Oh, Aang, it's good to see you.", "start": 327.411, "duration": 2.794}, {"text": "You haven't changed a bit.", "start": 330.539, "duration": 2.21}, {"text": "Literally.", "start": 333.417, "duration": 1.042}, {"text": "- Uh, over here!\n- Little help!", "start": 335.043, "duration": 2.461}, {"text": "[smashing]", "start": 338.964, "duration": 1.043}, {"text": "Jennamite is made of rock candy.", "start": 341.466, "duration": 2.044}, {"text": "Delicious!", "start": 344.636, "duration": 1.043}, {"text": "So this crazy king\nis your old friend Bumi?", "start": 346.013, "duration": 3.295}, {"text": "Who are you calling old?", "start": 349.6, "duration": 1.334}, {"text": "OK, I'm old.", "start": 351.685, "duration": 1.502}, {"text": "Why did you do all this instead of\njust telling Aang who you were?", "start": 353.478, "duration": 3.671}, {"text": "First of all,\nit's pretty fun messing with people.", "start": 357.399, "duration": 2.836}, {"text": "But I do have a reason.", "start": 361.57, "duration": 1.501}, {"text": "Aang, you have a difficult task ahead.", "start": 363.614, "duration": 2.544}, {"text": "The world has changed\nin the 100 years you've been gone.", "start": 366.45, "duration": 2.878}, {"text": "It's the duty of the Avatar\nto restore balance to the world", "start": 369.661, "duration": 3.212}, {"text": "by defeating Fire Lord Ozai.", "start": 372.956, "duration": 2.127}, {"text": "You have much to learn.", "start": 375.584, "duration": 1.209}, {"text": "You must master the four elements\nand confront the Fire Lord.", "start": 377.169, "duration": 3.587}, {"text": "And when you do,\nI hope you will think like a mad genius!", "start": 380.839, "duration": 4.129}, {"text": "And it looks like you're in good hands.", "start": 388.805, "duration": 2.628}, {"text": "You'll need your friends\nto help you defeat the Fire Nation.", "start": 391.725, "duration": 3.253}]